      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is always so busy and i feel like he just dismisses my concerns about the side effects... honestly i just want a more holistic approach. since st johns wort works on the same serotonin levels, wouldn't it just be a smooth transition if i just lower my dose of sertraline for a few days and then start the supplement? it seems pretty straightforward since they both do the same thing.",
