      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you on the safety thing, but i'm really just looking for some practical advice. if i'm really determined to do this because i can't wait weeks for an appointment, what's the most common way people do it? like, is there a specific tapering schedule or a certain dose of st johns wort that's considered \"standard\" to make sure there's no overlap? i just want to know what a typical transition looks like so i can feel more confident about doing it myself.",
